README (english)
--------------------------------


--------------------------------
Download
--------------------------------

* PowerERP ERP/CRM can be downloaded at sourceforge:
    https://sourceforge.net/projects/powererp/files
  or from PowerERP official web site:
    https://www.powererp.org

* Most external modules are only available on DoliStore:
    https://www.dolistore.com 


--------------------------------
Install
--------------------------------

* For a Quick guide, take a look at README.md file into root directory.

* More complete documentations are also available on line on the PowerERP Wiki:
    https://wiki.powererp.org
